Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.00,Utama,FEMALE STUDENT 1,0,0,0,,Serrvismu bagus, Yuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.16,Utama,FEMALE STUDENT 2,0,0,0,,Mantap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:11.61,Utama,YUKI,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.91,Utama,MALE STUDENT 1,0,0,0,,Semua yang dilakukan Yuki-san memukai sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:17.46,Utama,MALE STUDENT 2,0,0,0,,Sulit dipercaya dia sepantaran kita, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:19.56,Utama,MALE STUDENT 3,0,0,0,,Servisan maut Yuki-san lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:21.24,Utama,MALE STUDENTS,0,0,0,,Keren!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:24.75,Miring,HITOYOSHI {M},0,0,0,,Yah, tapi kemampuan asli Yuki-san jauh lebih dari itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:28.13,Utama,MALE STUDENT 1,0,0,0,,Sudah cantik, pintar, jago olahraga ....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:30.71,Utama,MALE STUDENT 1,0,0,0,,Sulit dipercaya dia kerabat Hitoyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:34.26,Miring,HITOYOSHI {M},0,0,0,,Yah, aku juga sependapat, sih ....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:41.99,Miring,HITOYOSHI {M},0,0,0,,Aku masih terpukau setelah melihat Yuki-san menolongku seperti di film-film.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:45.14,Kilas,GRACE {Flashback},0,0,0,,Dia adalah pembunuh keji berdarah dingin ....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:48.88,Kilas,GRACE {Flashback},0,0,0,,Sembilang Naga Keempat,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:50.90,Kilas,GRACE {Flashback},0,0,0,,Xue sang Serigala Putih.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:53.82,Kilas,YUKI {flashback},0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan membunuh siapapun lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:57.82,Kilas,YUKI {flashback},0,0,0,,Aku tidak ingin ada yang mati gara-gara aku.
