Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:16.84,Atas,HITOYOSHI,0,0,0,,Ada perlu apa, Bu Nitta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:18.44,Utama,GRACE,0,0,0,,Kenapa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:22.18,Utama,GRACE,0,0,0,,Tolong yang baik sama guru barumu yang kesepian, dong,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.79,Utama,GRACE,0,0,0,,Hitoyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:25.09,Utama,HITOYOSHI,0,0,0,,Dekat banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:28.22,Utama,HITOYOSHI,0,0,0,,Tolong jaga jarak antara guru dan murid!
